# EdgeMarkets Frontend Execution Rules

- Keep each source file under 550 LOC.
- Use Next.js App Router + TypeScript strict mode.
- Keep UI in focused components under `src/components`.
- Keep API calls in `src/lib/api.ts` only.
- Keep extension logic isolated under `extension/` (popup, background, content).
- Use clear names for handlers (`handleCreateStrategy`, `handleFollowStrategy`).
- Keep page UX fast: optimistic status updates and visible loading states.
- Avoid redundant docs and duplicate style systems.
